title: Girl At Home (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor's version sounds completely different than the stolen one... What was her inspo behind this song and why does it sound so different now? Plus, another awkward interview by Ellen and an epic red carpet mess up. We break it all down!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
